			<div class="content" id="post-content-3572798">
									

<p>It's a title in the organization. 'Minerval' was one of the three ranks in the original Bavarian Illuminati. I wanted to imply a similar hierarchy.</p>
<p>Minervan is derived from the name of the Roman goddess of wisdom. 'Illuminated' means 'enlightened' in this context, though it can also mean 'lit up brightly.'</p>

